description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'No Equipment 20 Minute Bodyweight Workout | Follow Along' from the channel JTM_FIT.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Today 's workout is a 20 minute full body workout that require ZERO equipment. All you will need is your bodyweight!

This is a full follow along workout that consists of 20 different exercises with no repeats.

We are going to perform each exercise for 45 seconds with 15 seconds rest in between exercises. 1 total set.

If you need to modify the workout you can do a few different time structures.
